00:34:56,230 --> 00:34:58,010
字幕
And Bruce Lee said, "I like that."

591
00:34:58,010 --> 00:35:01,360
字幕
- The way of the intercepting fist. - Intercepting fist?

592
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:05,030
字幕
It sounds Chinese, but it's very much an American martial art.

593
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:09,430
字幕
Jeet kune do was how can I most efficiently

594
00:35:09,430 --> 00:35:12,860
字幕
directly end a moment of combat?

595
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:22,200
字幕
The philosophy Bruce Lee had was:

596
00:35:22,200 --> 00:35:25,050
字幕
The simpler the better, the most effective, the direct line.

597
00:35:25,050 --> 00:35:27,610
字幕
- The other stuff was Hollywood. - It can be taught.

598
00:35:27,610 --> 00:35:30,880
字幕
- Do you understand? - But it cannot really be standardised.

599
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:34,090
字幕
And that's not to say that it can't be passed on.

600
00:35:34,090 --> 00:35:36,160
字幕
But it was very personal to him.

601
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:38,720
字幕
All the wannabes, all the imposters

602
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:41,930
字幕
who put up jeet kune do signs on their school building,

603
00:35:41,930 --> 00:35:44,730
字幕
and they have no idea whatjeet kune do is.

604
00:35:44,730 --> 00:35:45,890
字幕
They think it's a style.

605
00:35:45,890 --> 00:35:50,290
字幕
I don't know if he'd be dojo-busting in his days, but that would upset Bruce.

606
00:35:58,050 --> 00:36:01,900
字幕
Bruce Lee has the big middle finger raised toward any form of authority.

607
00:36:01,900 --> 00:36:04,750
字幕
All kinds of dogmas, all kinds of traditions.

608
00:36:04,750 --> 00:36:06,660
字幕
He's saying a big "screw you" to all of them.

609
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:10,570
字幕
