611
00:36:13,120 --> 00:36:16,680
字幕
In 1968 he says, "JKD in '69 will be different."

612
00:36:16,680 --> 00:36:19,680
字幕
I said, "This is really good stuff we're doing now."

613
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:24,200
字幕
He says, "JKD in '69 will be different. JKD in 1970 will be different."

614
00:36:24,200 --> 00:36:27,320
字幕
Martial arts has evolved more in the last ten years

615
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,730
字幕
than it has in the last 10,000 years,

616
00:36:29,730 --> 00:36:32,380
字幕
because all the stuff that Bruce Lee talked about

617
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:35,950
字幕
and his philosophies and things that he believed were finally proven

618
00:36:35,950 --> 00:36:39,940
字幕
and now this new martial art was able to start to grow and evolve.

619
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:43,770
字幕
Our main event, for the light heavyweight title,

620
00:36:43,770 --> 00:36:45,100
字幕
here we go!

621
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:49,600
字幕
