629
00:37:10,350 --> 00:37:13,730
字幕
I mean, the... everything, I mean, not just the hand.

630
00:37:16,620 --> 00:37:20,860
字幕
The crazy thing about martial arts is people debate and fight over this stuff.

631
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:21,820
字幕
