00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:59,980
字幕
When the UFC came in, they weren't talking about Bruce Lee.

665
00:38:59,980 --> 00:39:01,850
字幕
They were talking about Royce Gracie.

666
00:39:01,850 --> 00:39:04,370
字幕
Royce Gracie!

