682
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:55,000
字幕
Oh, man. That is the Karate Kid.

683
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:57,190
字幕
And when you're talking about combat...

684
00:39:57,190 --> 00:40:00,970
字幕
Well, I mean, if it is a sport, now you're talking about something else.

