00:40:07,690 --> 00:40:11,100
字幕
Well, then, baby, you'd better train every part of your body.

690
00:40:11,890 --> 00:40:15,220
字幕
Mixed martial art in the cage is for a contest. It's a sport.

691
00:40:15,220 --> 00:40:19,090
字幕
I don't know that I would call him exactly the father of mixed martial arts

