00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:04,540
字幕
Let's fight!

706
00:41:04,540 --> 00:41:09,890
字幕
It's the most hardcore real form of competition and honesty I could find,

707
00:41:09,890 --> 00:41:11,670
字幕
and that's the kind of thing I crave.

708
00:41:11,670 --> 00:41:14,670
字幕
Carano, a big-time puncher.

709
00:41:14,670 --> 00:41:17,020
字幕
There is fear. Sometimes you don't wanna go in there.

