00:43:17,330 --> 00:43:20,040
字幕
I believe that Bruce Lee was a huge fight fan.

750
00:43:20,040 --> 00:43:22,910
字幕
He'd have been jumping out of his seat, getting as excited as any of us.

751
00:43:22,910 --> 00:43:26,840
字幕
