00:43:50,750 --> 00:43:54,610
字幕
and you start talking about Bruce Lee, a lot of people get offended.

761
00:43:54,610 --> 00:43:57,620
字幕
People get pissed off and bombed out and everything else.

762
00:43:57,620 --> 00:44:02,100
字幕
But Bruce Lee is 100 percent the father of mixed martial arts.

763
00:44:08,550 --> 00:44:13,970
字幕
He was so directed and so concrete about his thoughts and his beliefs

